Class FieldValue<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.query.filter.expression.FieldValue<V>
  • Type Parameters:

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable, Expression<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanFieldValue, GenericFieldValue, NumericFieldValue, SpatialFieldValue, TemporalFieldValue, TextFieldValue

    public abstract class FieldValue<V>
extends Object
implements Expression<V>
    An abstract expression implementation for turning fields values from an adapter entry into an object to be used by the expression.
